title: 'Scream Queens' Cast Perfectly Spoofs Taylor Swift's Swiftmas!
text: Taylor Swift got a lot of buzz last year when she sent her fans Christmas gifts and now Emma Roberts is spoofing “Swiftmas” with this awesome new “Chanel-o-ween” video. The 24-year-old actress is seen in character as her Scream Queens character Chanel in the hilarious clip. “2015 was an amazing year for Chanel Oberlin and [...] »
